  "title": "Clinic Assistant / Exec",
  "description": "<p>Come join our dedicated team at <br /><strong>The Medical Clinic </strong>as <strong>Clinic Assistant!</strong></p><p>Great team, office-hours job, 5 mins from Raffles Place MRT</p><p><u><strong>Our Clinic</strong></u><br />We are a warm single practice General Practice, family clinic, at Raffles Place, right in the Central Business District. Whilst serving patients in the midst of the central business area, our Clinic Assistants and doctors believe in providing sincere and good care to all our patients.</p><p>Our current team of dedicated Clinic Assistants have all worked with us for many years. Our staff work well as a team and we treat each other like family. Above all, we uphold the values of honesty, integrity and care.</p><p>We are looking for dedicated Clinic Assistants to help us with the following work:</p><p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><p>-Clinic reception: registration, managing calls, discharge, payment</p><p>-E-administration, e-claims, billings, ordering of medicine/supplies</p><p>-Assistance with e-consults and preparation of medicine for delivery</p><p>-Arranging for appointments at clinic or referrals</p><p>-Contacting patients for lab results</p><p><strong>Requirements for our Clinic Assistants:</strong></p><p>-2 years experience at a GP clinic will be an advantage</p><p>-Admin skills with customer service an advantage</p><p>-Must be IT savvy</p><p>-Speak good English, mandarin will be advantage</p><p>-Strong communicator</p><p>-Team player and customer orientated.</p><p>Full time role: Mon-Fri 8:30am - 5:30am; alternate Sat 8:30am-1pm</p>",
